###  회원 목록 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/library/members

###  회원 목록 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/library/members?name=없음

### 회원 단건 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/library/members/10

### 회원 등록
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/library/members
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "reader05",
  "name": "",
  "email": "email@naver.com"
}

###  도서 목록 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/library/books

###  도서 목록 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/library/books?title=Spring&status=AVAILABLE

### 도서 단권 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/library/books/5

### 도서 등록
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/library/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Spring REST API 입문",
  "author": "오지라퍼",
  "isbn": "979-11-1111-111-1",
  "publishedAt": "2025-03-10"
}

###  대여 목록 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/library/rentals

###  대여 단건 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/library/rentals/2

### 대여 등록
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/library/rentals
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "memberNo": 5,
  "bookNo": 4
}

### 도서 반납
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/library/rentals/2/return
